### Sample requests — use with the VS Code REST Client extension or as curl refs.
@host = http://localhost:8080

### Create an event (202 Accepted, returns pending event)
POST {{host}}/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Click",
  "source": "web",
  "payload": { "value": 21, "page": "/pricing" }
}

### Validation failure (422 with field-level details)
POST {{host}}/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{ "type": "" }

### Get one event by id (replace the id)
GET {{host}}/v1/events/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### List processed events, paginated
GET {{host}}/v1/events?status=processed&limit=10&offset=0

### Aggregate stats
GET {{host}}/v1/stats

### Health / readiness / metrics
GET {{host}}/healthz

###
GET {{host}}/readyz

###
GET {{host}}/metrics
